ification', '1', '4'), ('32', 'An Observer based Open Circuit fault Detection for Switches of PMSM Drive', 'https://ietresearch.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/cms/asset/9856e4a5-d306-457c-8391-99a6ecb08ceb/tje212073-fig-0009-m.jpg', 'Identifies open-circuit faults in PMSM motor drives via observer-based diagnostic systems.', '', 'https://github.com/SMarjanAlavi/OC_FDI_EXP27State7W', '1', '4'), ('33', 'Arduino Based Smart Illuminated Display', 'https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.WyZUxYMoEioAuDZTbdfsjQAAAA?rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain', 'Controls programmable LED displays using Arduino for dynamic signage solutions.', '', 'https://github.com/heybenchen/lumi', '1', '4'), ('34', 'RFID based book shelling system', 'https://cpcongroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/RFID-Based-Book-Tracking-System-for-Libraries-768x439.webp', 'Automates library book sorting and tracking using RFID technology.', '', 'https://github.com/Deshan555/RFID_Based_Library-System-For_Book_Return', '1', '4'), ('35', 'IOT based Grow light farming', 'https://img.freepik.com/premium-photo/revolutionizing-sustainable-urban-agriculture-with-vertical-farming-led-grow-lights-hydroponics-ai-automation-concept-sustainable-urban-agriculture-vertical-farming-led-grow-lights_918839-185764.jpg', 'Optimizes indoor farming with IoT-controlled grow lights for plant growth cycles.', '', 'https://github.com/Kartikay77/Smart-Farming-using-IoT', '1', '4'), ('36', 'Multi functional agricultural machine using IOT', 'https://image.made-in-china.com/2f0j00gAIoHmPRfMcq/Mini-Tractor-Weima-Wmx620-1-Cultivator-Power-Tiller-Multi-Function-Agricultural-Machine-Rotary-Tiller-Gasoline-Engine-Trencher-Self-Propelled.jpg', 'Develops a multifunctional IoT agricultural machine for plowing, seeding, and harvesting.', '', 'https://github.com/atharval1/precision-agriculture-using-machine-learning', '1', '4'), ('37', 'Smart Waste Management', 'https://www.themayor.eu/web/files/articles/1879/main_image/thumb_1024x663_Bin.png', 'Implements smart bins with fill-l