://daxg39y63pxwu.cloudfront.net/images/blog/machine-learning-case-studies/Customer_Churn_Prediction_Machine_Learning_Case_Study.png', 'Forecasts customer attrition risks using behavioral data and predictive analytics.', '', 'https://github.com/Sameer-ansarii/Customer-Churn-Prediction', '2', '4'), ('55', 'Credit Card Fraud Detection Using Anomaly Detection', 'https://www.xenonstack.com/hubfs/xenonstack-credit-card-fraud-detection.png', 'Identifies fraudulent credit card transactions via anomaly detection in spending patterns.', '', 'https://github.com/curiousily/Credit-Card-Fraud-Detection-using-Autoencoders-in-Keras', '2', '4'), ('56', 'Sentiment Analysis of Product Reviews', 'https://miro.medium.com/max/1200/1*TUqC3XRqvzErhnFC4h1Rcw@2x.png', 'Evaluates customer opinions in product reviews using NLP-based sentiment classification.', '', 'https://github.com/shayanzare007/EntitySentiment', '2', '4'), ('57', 'Disease Prediction Using Medical Data', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/5Ex8eAuCcCU/maxresdefault.jpg', 'Predicts disease risks (e.g., diabetes, heart conditions) using patient health records and ML.', '', 'https://github.com/anujdutt9/Disease-Prediction-from-Symptoms', '2', '4'), ('58', 'Movie Recommendation System Using Collaborative Filtering', 'https://editor.analyticsvidhya.com/uploads/76889recommender-system-for-movie-recommendation.jpg', 'Recommends movies based on user preferences and collaborative filtering algorithms.', '', 'https://github.com/asif536/Movie-Recommender-System', '2', '4'), ('59', 'Air Quality Prediction Using Machine Learning', 'https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/122162103/256710306-157d72a6-6151-4564-a5ea-962413b413ff.png', 'Forecasts air pollution levels (PM2.5, CO) using environmental sensors and ML models.', '', 'https://github.com/anillava1999/Air-Quality-Prediction', '2', '4'), ('60', 'E-commerce Sales Forecasting Using Time Series Analysis', 'https://digitalschoolofmarketing.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/shutterstock_1401229571-e